{"tid":802146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有中國人網上留言 從招商銀行得知 美元額度已從5萬美元下降到2萬","createTime":"2018-09-01T08:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T08:58:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45a0ccfdcdf32b72a908270953218ccaf6b7502c","tid":802146,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:45:34.000Z","msg":"真希望這是胡言亂語，一再強力讓自己鎮定，不要慌亂。可是前天我親自去招商銀行咨詢，美元額度已經從人均5萬降到2萬了。而中共政策是隨時更改的。這銳降一多半的額度也沒公告或通知誰。<br />\n我在銀行還明知故問會不會有一天強制結匯？工作人員當然說不會。<br />\n走出銀行，穿梭在車水馬龍，心裡淒淒然。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我親自去招行，當時的大堂經理給我解答。我當時有點急事，沒再深問，好像取現鈔和存匯有所區別。存匯已經從原先的五萬降到兩萬是確定的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/rain8909/status/1035787778271793152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Frain8909%2Fstatus%2F1035787778271793152&d=P3lOVsx1LOMrVFA5p5kvI04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=f02be9a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/rain8909/status/1035787778271793152</a>"},{"pid":"8c1dcc984ceb00b7430be9303139a5ae1e546fbb","tid":802146,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:46:45.000Z","msg":"頭盔：唔知真假<br />\n或者喺中國做野巴打可以問吓銀行查證吓"},{"pid":"ac75a35fa3465f9d08b24e00011ed5972afd5086","tid":802146,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:47:09.000Z","msg":"真係冇曬錢就打仗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e32311b14fe91f7d771f94589e8733be9cf37b4","tid":802146,"uid":153778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"早兩年大6人黎香港買樓買保險走資太勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等睇AA狗保險雞全家生性病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}